org.wildfly.security.util

Class NumericIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wildfly.security.util.NumericIterator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ByteIterator, CodePointIterator

    abstract class NumericIterator
extends Object
    Non-public numeric iterator base class. It is important to keep this non-public to prevent type confusion between byte and code point iterators, which are fundamentally incompatible.
    Author:
    David M. Lloyd
